<h1 id="toc1"><span>So, are you confused because there isn't <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/component:anomaly-class-bar">ACS</a> icons you want to use?</span></h1>
<h3 id="toc2"><span>Hei ! Here are m-o-r-e Secondary Class icons.</span></h3>
<hr />
<h2 id="toc3"><span>How to use them in Esoteric Classes ?<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-1')">1</a></sup></span></h2>
<h3 id="toc4"><span>Remember to use lowercase letters, bro.</span></h3>
<div class="help">
<blockquote>
<p>Beginning of include ↦</p>
<p>Item # of SCP ↦</p>
<p>Clearance Level <em>USE DIGITS (5,4,3,2,1,0)</em> (<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/anomaly-classification-system-guide">See guide</a>)↦</p>
<p>Container Class (Also known as Object Class) ↦</p>
<p>OPTIONAL Secondary Class (If Using, set Container Class to <em>Esoteric</em>) ↦</p>
<p>If secondary class is used, place URL here ↦</p>
<p>Disruption Class (<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/anomaly-classification-system-guide">See Guide</a> &amp; Read Below for Explanation) ↦</p>
<p>Risk Class (<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/anomaly-classification-system-guide">See Guide</a> &amp; Read Below for Explanation) ↦</p>
<p>End of include ↦</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><tt>[[<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">include</span> :scp-wiki:component:anomaly-class-bar-source</tt></p>
<p><tt>|item-number= XXXX</tt></p>
<p><tt>|clearance= #</tt></p>
<p><tt>|container-class= euclid</tt></p>
<p><tt>|secondary-class= none</tt></p>
<p><tt>|secondary-icon= <a href="http://urlhere.com">http://urlhere.com</a></tt></p>
<p><tt>|disruption-class= vlam</tt></p>
<p><tt>|risk-class= warning</tt></p>
<p><tt>]]</tt></p>
</blockquote>
</div>
